    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Brainstorm Your Project\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to explore ideas for your project based on your selected SDG target. The bot will provide examples, key facts, and real-world challenges to help you think critically about possible solutions.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nUse these questions to guide your conversation:\r\n\r\n* What are some examples of ______ in the real world?\r\n* Why is ______ an important issue?\r\n* What challenges do people face related to ______?\r\n* How could technology help solve ______?\r\n* What kinds of sensors or data could be used to address ______?\r\n* How might a computer system (hardware, software, network) be designed to improve ______?",
